title: Homestyle Japanese Omurice | オムライス | Fried Rice Friday #4
description:
Omurice is one of the most popular Japanese home-cooked dishes. This fourth (and final - for now) instalment of Fried Rice Fridays is a simple fried rice known as “chicken rice” covered in a soft-set omelette and demi-glace sauce. There are three main styles of preparing the omelette for the omurice, and this is the most popular one.
